00:12:11,260 --> 00:12:15,140
With just an arrow.

147
00:12:18,090 --> 00:12:20,200
When it collapses, the person
standing beneath it

148
00:12:20,330 --> 00:12:23,310
should reach kingdom come.

149
00:12:28,230 --> 00:12:30,210
Will you be able
to fulfill the plan?

150
00:12:31,190 --> 00:12:33,070
Who is this meant for,
king of Gandhar?

151
00:12:34,230 --> 00:12:36,140
For the one

152
00:12:38,330 --> 00:12:42,270
who Duryodhan may
not be able to defeat.

153
00:13:13,190 --> 00:13:16,200
Are you making arrangements for
the test, son? - No, father.

154
00:13:18,090 --> 00:13:20,270
I am making arrangements to
make my friend Duryodhan win.

155
00:13:23,190 --> 00:13:26,260
You would have benefited, had
you befriended Arjun, son.

156
00:13:29,230 --> 00:13:30,260
The scriptures say

157
00:13:32,130 --> 00:13:35,040
one should always befriend
someone who is more intelligent

158
00:13:35,230 --> 00:13:37,100
or more powerful than you.

159
00:13:39,090 --> 00:13:41,160
Such friendship ends
in animosity.

160
00:13:45,030 --> 00:13:46,200
There is one more
important thing.

161
00:13:47,030 --> 00:13:48,160
The one who is the best

162
00:13:48,230 --> 00:13:50,230
never needs anyone.

163
00:13:51,030 --> 00:13:52,200
Thus, he's merciful

164
00:13:53,160 --> 00:13:54,260
and doesn't befriend anyone.

165
00:13:55,230 --> 00:13:58,000
I and Duryodhan
need each other.

166
00:13:58,130 --> 00:14:02,100
He needs my help to attain
the throne of Hastinapur.

167
00:14:02,190 --> 00:14:03,260
That's impossible.

168
00:14:07,990 --> 00:14:10,030
The heir of Hastinapur

169
00:14:10,190 --> 00:14:12,190
will be appointed
based on eligibility.

170
00:14:12,230 --> 00:14:13,230
And eligibility

171
00:14:14,130 --> 00:14:16,200
cannot be proven with
somebody's help.

172
00:14:16,990 --> 00:14:18,990
To me, this is an opportunity

173
00:14:19,990 --> 00:14:22,970
to make my friendship
with Duryodhan stronger.

174
00:14:24,090 --> 00:14:26,090
