a king in the future

175
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:29,030
Hastinapur should
stand to protect me.

176
00:14:34,090 --> 00:14:35,130
Father.

177
00:14:37,090 --> 00:14:39,230
I have spent my life considering
a mixture of flour as milk.

178
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:44,070
I never asked for anything.
I never objected to anything.

179
00:14:45,130 --> 00:14:46,200
But today, I ask of you.

180
00:14:47,230 --> 00:14:50,000
Whatever happens in the
competition held for the princes

181
00:14:50,160 --> 00:14:52,140
let it happen the way it is.

182
00:14:57,160 --> 00:14:58,970
Son...

183
00:15:00,190 --> 00:15:03,000
I cannot be unrighteous for you.

184
00:15:03,060 --> 00:15:04,940
But you can at least keep quiet.

185
00:15:07,930 --> 00:15:09,910
I need your assurance

186
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:11,100
that you will keep quiet.

187
00:15:12,190 --> 00:15:14,000
And you will let

188
00:15:14,960 --> 00:15:16,130
things happen the way they are.

189
