Attention!

194
00:16:10,480 --> 00:16:14,390
King Dhritarashtra
is on his way!

195
00:16:16,310 --> 00:16:18,290
I was waiting for this day

196
00:16:18,510 --> 00:16:21,290
since the last twelve
years, Your Majesty.

197
00:16:21,340 --> 00:16:24,380
And you have promised
that this day

198
00:16:25,340 --> 00:16:27,450
will be the most happiest day
of my life, Shakuni.

199
00:16:28,310 --> 00:16:32,420
I am sure there is nothing
lacking in your arrangements.

200
00:16:32,510 --> 00:16:34,490
If my nephews are hailed
by the people

201
00:16:35,440 --> 00:16:38,390
only then this day would be
the happiest day for me, O king.

202
00:16:38,410 --> 00:16:42,480
And I never make mistakes
for the sake of my happiness.

203
00:17:20,340 --> 00:17:24,420
Greetings, sister.
- Come Kunti, sit here

204
00:17:25,210 --> 00:17:26,240
next to me.

205
00:17:28,210 --> 00:17:31,420
Today, I want to see my
sons with your eyes.

206
00:17:33,310 --> 00:17:35,380
I mean, your sons too.

207
00:17:37,410 --> 00:17:39,250
Greetings, aunt Kunti.

208
00:17:41,180 --> 00:17:42,280
Bless you, Dushala.

209
00:17:43,240 --> 00:17:46,380
Aren't you anxious to watch
the prowess of your brothers?

210
00:17:47,280 --> 00:17:48,380
I am really excited.

211
00:17:51,310 --> 00:17:54,380
Long live king Dhritarashtra!

212
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:58,320
Long live king Dhritarashtra!

213
00:17:59,410 --> 00:18:00,390
Subjects!

214
00:18:02,210 --> 00:18:05,250
Today many brave Aryan kings

215
00:18:05,410 --> 00:18:08,320
and princes have arrived
in Hastinapur

216
00:18:08,380 --> 00:18:11,410
to witness the strength of the
new generation of the Kurus.

217
00:18:13,280 --> 00:18:16,350
To get introduced to the
strength of the Kuru dynasty

218
00:18:18,140 --> 00:18:20,320
I welcome everyone
to Hastinapur.

219
00:18:22,240 --> 00:18:23,350
Today on this playground

220
00:18:23,410 --> 00:18:26,180
bravery and potential
would be exhibited.

221
00:18:26,280 --> 00:18:29,220
And it shall reverberate in all
corners of the earth.

222
00:18:29,340 --> 00:18:32,260
The praises would be heard

223
00:18:33,140 --> 00:18:35,250
till the end of time!

224
00:18:35,410 --> 00:18:39,220
Today, on this playground
a new history would begin.

225
00:18:39,240 --> 00:18:42,190
The future of the
divine nation established

226
00:18:42,310 --> 00:18:46,260
by the great Kuru ancestors
shall be decided.

